@page
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Terms of Service";
    Layout = "_Layout";
}

<div class="atz-card p-4 legal-page">
    <h1 class="atz-section-title">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-muted">Last updated: @DateTime.UtcNow.ToString("MMMM yyyy")</p>

    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">1. Service</h2>
    <p>A to Z Clinical provides clinic management software on a subscription basis. Access is granted per clinic tenant and authorized users only.</p>

    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">2. Accounts &amp; security</h2>
    <p>You are responsible for safeguarding login credentials and for activity under your clinic accounts. Notify us promptly of unauthorized access.</p>

    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">3. Subscription &amp; billing</h2>
    <p>Paid plans renew monthly unless canceled. Trials convert to paid plans before expiration to avoid interruption. Fees are non-refundable except where required by law.</p>

    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">4. Acceptable use</h2>
    <p>You may not misuse the service, attempt to access other tenants' data, or upload malicious content. Clinical data must be handled according to applicable privacy laws.</p>

    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">5. Data ownership</h2>
    <p>Your clinic retains ownership of patient and operational data entered into the system. We process data only to provide and secure the service.</p>

    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">6. Limitation of liability</h2>
    <p>The service is provided "as is" to the maximum extent permitted by law. We are not liable for indirect or consequential damages arising from use of the platform.</p>

    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">7. Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about these terms: contact your system vendor or the address listed on your clinic invoice.</p>
</div>
